text: Cikota ca AI hapwile kaakucikilikicila kandji ku kuthuala ku upite, kuwka, kumana auswalale ngwe cizecene anacithungu ku ihela iekhanhiyekha ize ia cisaji ca kusonekenanhikulithacika ca izulie.

English: The Chokwe people are the descendants of the Chokwe people who lived in the area of the present day Chokwe, Kenya.

text: Mwemusono lume kaanalingi, alioze cilinhiulemu cize anakathulika izulie yayo hanga ipwe cihingo hakusoloka ca cize japwa je shizo jaku kopanajo uzulie ya mu ngazo jize jahapwile.

text: Ayino yishi uika kutulueza tushitu akuo dinossauros yapua nhi mana amo uika uaze akuamba,mba naua yina tuaha uteso,ua fosseis ayo keshi kuhasa, ngue naua anji cor ya disposicao tridimensional.

text: Cihela cize ca Turquia kuwezelako Lagos cinambata 783,562 cha quilometros cuadrado (300,948 sq mi) ku kuze 755,688 kilometros cuadrados (291,773 sq mi) katwama kuthuto wa Asia nhi 23,764 kilometros quadrados (9,174 sq mi) mu Europa.
translated_text: Chokwe: Cihela cize ca Turquia kuwezelako Lagos cinambata 783,562 cha quilometros cuadrado (300,948 sq mi) ku kuze 755,688 kilometros cuadrados (291,773 sq mi) katwama kuthuto wa Asia nhi 23,764 kilometros quadrados (9,174 sq mi) mu Europa. English: Lagos, Nigeria.

text: Mailha Shetland ya kutho, anakawana ha 1819, kali akuhangulula kuli ifuci indji nhi kali anene kwalula ya base, ya kumi issambano anakalakala ha 2020.
translated_text: Chokwe: Mailha Shetland ya kutho, anakawana ha 1819, kali akuhangulula kuli ifuci indji nhi kali anene kwalula ya base, ya kumi issambano anakalakala ha 2020. English: The Shetland Islands are a group of islands in the North Atlantic Ocean, in the British Isles.

text: Apia ili capital iya Samoa, mbongue ili mu ilha iya Upolonhiili amue athu iya kakumi mukehe mwixi iya 40.000 habitantes.
